data.revised_prompt: A high-resolution photograph of a cyberpunk city at night, featuring a bustling street illuminated by vibrant neon lights. The scene includes several flying vehicles at various altitudes, adding to the futuristic atmosphere. The architecture of the buildings is modern and sleek, with some buildings displaying neon signs. The street is wet, reflecting the neon lights and creating a misty, atmospheric environment. The focus is on the cityscape without any distracting foreground elements, ensuring the neon-lit streets and flying vehicles are the central features of the image. The overall composition is designed to emphasize the vibrant, nocturnal essence of the cyberpunk setting.
